            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top"><strong><em>Interlitq’s</em> “The Groves of Academe” series: </strong><br><br>

<strong>Interview with <a href="http://interlitq.org/issue3/zulfikar_ghose/bio.php">Zulfikar Ghose</a>,<bR><br>

Professor Emeritus, the University of Texas at Austin,
<bR><br>
